{"id": "1470313287731253300", "channel_id": "1470313287731253300", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "溅在漆黑帷幕上的第一滴血，宣告了这场杀戮游戏的开始。\n凄惨的死者，幽闭的列车，猜忌的种子已经悄悄种下。\n「可是……为什么会是她？」\n\n<:question2:1356053130336272414> 守密人觉得这场游戏的第一名牺牲者会是谁呢？请在评论区留下您的推测吧！\n答案揭晓后，小N将在评论区分享「银芯×200」兑换码，作为与各位乘客的见面礼！\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\nV2.4.2 The First Bloodstain\n\nThe first splash of crimson hits the velvet curtain. The killing game has officially begun.\nA tragic victim. A sealed train. The seeds of suspicion have already taken root.\n\"Of all people... why her?\"\n\n<:question2:1356053130336272414> Keepers, who do you think will be the first to fall in this deadly game? Drop your guess in the comments below!\nOnce the truth is revealed, Little N will share a \"Silver×200\" redemption code in the comments as a greeting gift to all passengers!", "timestamp": "2026-02-09T07:00:04.895000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "W_falldown", "emoji_id": "1400771812542906389", "count": 17}, {"emoji": "bow", "emoji_id": "1356053037159944473", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "thinking1", "emoji_id": "1356068128936820929", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "cry3", "emoji_id": "1356082134447558748", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1470313289056784539", "filename": "1.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 3126679, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1470313287731253300/1470313289056784539/1.png?ex=69ccc275&is=69cb70f5&hm=36e3343777428776ca804d1fddbd0eb5cb0f22650041c40a9f29754571b5c28d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1470313287731253300", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.4.2 第一块血迹┊The First Bloodstain", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1357267957901951088", "1357267999253467207"]}
